    - added Option for requesting before changing destination
    - some changes in documents
  
  Revision V2.21
  --------------
  created on Wednesday, 04.05.94 by Stefan Schulz
    - removed ugly Bug which caused tooltypes not being kept
    - changed register-handling, so colors are correct even with os3-icons
    - changed Source-Field-Background, smaller Dest-Field
    - removed Bug loading icons via menu didn't work selecting .info-files
  
